<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n11156a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11156a">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11156a"> 156(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> her d. Alix m Pierre / de Dreux / 1215 / 4th Capet dynasty </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Alix was the daughter of Geoffrey, duke of Brittany. She married Pierre de Dreux, a prince of the Capetian dynasty, in 1212. In the following year he became duke of Brittany and thereby founder of a line of French dukes of Brittany, a line that lasted until the end of the fifteenth century. </mm> </dd></dl>
